# Example: House Price Prediction

Suppose we have the following data:

| House Size | Price     |
| ---------- | --------- |
| 1000 sq.ft | ₹20 Lakhs |
| 1500 sq.ft | ₹30 Lakhs |
| 2000 sq.ft | ₹40 Lakhs |

The machine learns the relationship between house size and price.

When a new house size is given:

House Size = 1800 sq.ft

The model predicts the expected price.

